","text":{"content":"High road speeds that generate heat or high load capabilities like heavy transport tankers or trailers","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"High road speeds that generate heat or high load capabilities like heavy transport tankers or trailers","href":null}]]},"archived":false}]},{"object":"block","id":"38234d6d-7cea-81d4-947d-d982104579d5","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"38234d6d-7cea-812d-96b4-c0ce1f9c67d9"},"created_time":"2026-06-17T19:19:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-06-17T19:19:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"heading_2","heading_2":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Radial Tires in Agriculture","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Radial Tires in Agriculture","href":null}],"is_toggleable":false,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"38234d6d-7cea-8172-b23e-f0576c0189ef","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"38234d6d-7cea-812d-96b4-c0ce1f9c67d9"},"created_time":"2026-06-17T19:19:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-06-17T19:19:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"As agricultural machinery continues to grow in weight and engine horsepower, nylon radial casing with steel belts or steel casing with steel belts is increasingly common.\n\nIn addition, compact construction equipment is becoming a staple of agriculture to support all farming operations.  Over the last 25 years, skid steers and backhoes have become integral parts of any farm or grower’s operation. Telehandlers, wheeled excavators, and compact wheel loaders are a few more pieces of equipment that are popping up in agriculture, especially in Europe. Smaller farms with tighter road restrictions rely heavily on radial tires due to the high load and high transport speeds required.\n\nSome examples of our own radial construction tire offerings include:","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"As agricultural machinery continues to grow in weight and engine horsepower, nylon radial casing with steel belts or steel casing with steel belts is increasingly common.\n\nIn addition, compact construction equipment is becoming a staple of agriculture to support all farming operations.  Over the last 25 years, skid steers and backhoes have become integral parts of any farm or grower’s operation. Telehandlers, wheeled excavators, and compact wheel loaders are a few more pieces of equipment that are popping up in agriculture, especially in Europe. Smaller farms with tighter road restrictions rely heavily on radial tires due to the high load and high transport speeds required.\n\nSome examples of our own radial construction tire offerings include:","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"38234d6d-7cea-81ce-8423-cad4e82a1913","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"38234d6d-7cea-812d-96b4-c0ce1f9c67d9"},"created_time":"2026-06-17T19:19:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-06-17T19:19:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"image","image":{"caption":[],"type":"external","external":{"url":"https://maxamtire.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/question-24-3-800x571.png"}},"archived":false},{"object":"blo